    - target: {fileID: 8221346256009138005, guid: 78ecf8c73ec0561459e0bdc5b6cbac07, type: 3}
      propertyPath: noteTitle
      value: October 19th - Peeling
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 8221346256009138005, guid: 78ecf8c73ec0561459e0bdc5b6cbac07, type: 3}
      propertyPath: noteContent
      value: '(The handwriting is jagged, heavily smeared with dark red fingerprints)

        They
        are under the skin. The frequencies. I had to let them out.

        I used
        the letter opener. It wasn''t enough. The ticking is louder now, deafening.

        It''s
        not a machine. It''s a voice.

        The tall watcher in the living room...
        it told me how to stop the noise. But I need to hear the truth first.'
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
