    m_Modifications:
    - target: {fileID: 456278349507124882, guid: 6f10ab1ceeb9cdb40aedfd324e4f6002, type: 3}
      propertyPath: noteTitle
      value: (Illegible / Unhinged scribbles)
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 456278349507124882, guid: 6f10ab1ceeb9cdb40aedfd324e4f6002, type: 3}
      propertyPath: noteContent
      value: '(The page is almost entirely soaked in dried blood. The words are carved
        deep into the paper)

        I RECORDED IT. I CAUGHT THE DEMON''S BREATH
        ON TAPE.

        If you are reading this, DO NOT LISTEN TO IT.

        I
        buried it. I buried the cassette in the dark belly below this very page.

        The
        left twin swallowed it whole. Let it starve. LET IT STARVE.

        My ears
        are bleeding. God, make it stop.'
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
